<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8"/>
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Edit</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" id="applicationStylesheet" href="/css/registerAdmin.css"/>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.16.0/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <!-- JS -->
    <script id="applicationScript" type="text/javascript" src="/js/register.js"></script>
    <!-- jQuery -->
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>

</head>
<body >

<div id="SignUp">
    <img id="bg_img" src="/img/registerAdmin/bkregister.jpg" srcset="/img/registerAdmin/bkregister.jpg 1x">
    </svg>
    <svg class="bg_shadow_l">
        <linearGradient id="bg_shadow_l" spreadMethod="pad" x1="0.5" x2="0.5" y1="0" y2="1">
            <stop offset="0" stop-color="#000" stop-opacity="0.678"></stop>
            <stop offset="1" stop-color="#000" stop-opacity="0.612"></stop>
        </linearGradient>
        <rect id="bg_shadow_l" rx="0" ry="0" x="0" y="0" width="1920" height="1080">
        </rect>
    </svg>
    <svg class="div_form">
        <rect id="div_form" rx="0" ry="0" x="0" y="0" width="1440" height="860">
        </rect>
    </svg>
    <svg class="div_regData">
        <rect id="div_regData" rx="0" ry="0" x="0" y="0" width="860" height="860">
        </rect>
    </svg>
    <div id="txt_note">
        <span>Al tener un perfil de usuario el mismo acepta nuestros términos y condiciones de uso.</span>
    </div>
    <div id="txt_titleForm">
        <span>Editar</span>
    </div>
    <div id="txt_info">
            <span>Edita los datos para poder actualizar en nuestro sitio web el perfil del usuario.
            </span>
    </div>
    <img id="sideForm_img" src="/img/registerAdmin/loro.jpg" srcset="/img/registerAdmin/loro.jpg 1x">
    <img id="Logo" src="/img/register/Logo.png" srcset="/img/register/Logo.png 1x" >
    <div class="form" >
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <form id="editarUser"
                      action="/editarUser"
                      method="POST"
                      oninput='password_login2.setCustomValidity(password_login2.value !== password_login.value ? "Passwords do not match." : "")'>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <% if (messages.success) { %>
                            <div class="alert alert-success" role="alert">
                                <%= messages.success %>
                            </div>
                        <% } %>
                        <% if (messages.error) { %>
                            <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">
                                <%= messages.error %>
                            </div>
                        <% } %>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-lg" id="formGroupNOMBREInput"
                                required name="nombre" value="" placeholder="<%= nombre %>">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-lg" id="formGroupAPELLIDOInput"
                               placeholder="<%= apellido %>" required name="apellido">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input type="email" class="email form-control form-control-lg" id="email"
                                pattern="[a-z0-9._%+-]+@[a-z0-9.-]+\.[a-z]{2,4}$"
                               required name="usuario_login" placeholder="<%= correo %>">
                        <div class="valid-feedback feedback-pos">
                            Looks good!
                        </div>
                        <div class="invalid-feedback feedback-pos">
                            Please input valid email ID
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input type="password" class="form-control form-control-lg" id="formGroupPASSInput"
                               aria-describedby="passwordHelpBlock" required name="password_login" pattern=".{8,}"
                               title="8 characters minimun" placeholder="Ingrese nueva contraseña">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input type="password" class="form-control form-control-lg" id="formGroupREPASSInput"
                               aria-describedby="passwordHelpBlock" required name="password_login2" placeholder="Confirmar contraseña">
                        <small id="passwordHelpBlock" class="form-text text-muted">
                            Your password must be 8-20 characters long, contain letters and numbers, and must not
                            contain spaces,
                            special characters, or emoji.
                        </small>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" value="validate" class="btn btn-danger text-uppercase sbmt-btn col-3 col-md-2 col-lg-4 ml-1" id="btn_submit">
                        Guardar
                    </button>
                    <hr>


                </form>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</div>


</body>
</html>